[SN]TITLE[SN]
Your rainbow pictures from around the world

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
After hours of rainfall, residents of Beijing were treated to a stunning rainbow which dominated the city skyline on Monday.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It was an unusual sight for many, as the Chinese capital is normally shrouded in smog.
You have been sending in your pictures of rainbows taken around the world. Take a look at our selection.
